### xBloom API — example requests (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP)
@base = http://localhost:8080
# After running "Login", paste the token here:
@token = PASTE_TOKEN

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Login (Admin / 0001)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Admin", "pin": "0001" }

### Who am I
GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Register a warranty (public)
POST {{base}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serial": "XB-9001",
  "product": "xBloom Studio",
  "purchaseDate": "2025-06-01",
  "name": "ทดสอบ ลูกค้า",
  "phone": "0801112222",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "postal": "10110"
}

### Check coverage (public)
GET {{base}}/coverage/XB-9001

### Create a ticket (public)
POST {{base}}/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serial": "XB-0001",
  "name": "สมชาย",
  "phone": "0812345678",
  "issueType": "ไม่จ่ายน้ำ",
  "description": "เปิดติดแต่ไม่จ่ายน้ำ",
  "repairType": "warranty"
}

### Track a ticket (public — no internal notes)
GET {{base}}/tickets/TK-20250601-0001

### List tickets (staff)
GET {{base}}/tickets?status=new
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Advance ticket status
PATCH {{base}}/tickets/TK-20250601-0001/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "diagnose", "note": "เริ่มตรวจเครื่อง" }

### Assign / notes
PATCH {{base}}/tickets/TK-20250601-0001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "assignedTo": "Tech", "staffNote": "นัดรับเครื่อง" }

### Dashboard summary
GET {{base}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Machines (assets) — list store assets
GET {{base}}/machines?assetType=store
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Machine history
GET {{base}}/machines/XB-0001/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Products
GET {{base}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Export CSV
GET {{base}}/export/csv?type=warranties
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Activity log
GET {{base}}/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Global claims (month filter)
GET {{base}}/global-claims?month=2025-06
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete warranty (admin re-auth via header)
DELETE {{base}}/warranties/SOME-ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
x-admin-pin: 0001
